				<td colspan="2"><span>We did not have enough folks initially so we proceeded to take on some of the mini's. 
<br />

<br />
After a mini-wipe, another guild offered to help. However, after much time in moving everyone to Tarlang's location, someone trained the raid and almost wiped everyone. 
<br />

<br />
After that some folks left and after reviewing the numbers, we just did not have it to take him down.
<br />

<br />
EQ2 has certainly attracted many people as my friends list and the log of top guilds has been cut in half. So trying to recruit more folks last night proved to be very difficult.
<br />

<br />
I will post again when we look to doing this again. 
